text: Tamim Iqbal Khan popularly known as Tamim Iqbal () (born 20 March 1989) is a Bangladeshi cricketer. Tamim made his One Day International and Test debut at 2007. He is a left-handed opening batsman and was the captain of Bangladesh national cricket team from March 2020 to August 2023. == References == ==Other websites== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:People from Chittagong Division
